name: MS Real - Mating Press LoRA
description:
Do you want to support me? Consider being a patron on Patreon to vote on train polls and access stuff early. ❤️

MS Real is a new collection I'll be doing. Instead of Anime images like I do normally in "Murky's" MS Real will be focussed on realistic models. So far as I tested it works on anime models too.

Trained with 30 images and 768x768.

Use 512x and hires fix for better results

Tags you might need are

1girl, 1boy, hetero, penis,testicles, sex, mating press, anus, pussy, ass, solo focus, vaginal, lying, on back, spread legs

Use the LoRA weight around 0.8 and 1 for the best results

Known Problems

-Sometime It refuses to draw penis

-Because of really small dataset I flipped images (Original 15 Flipped 30) and because of that time to time it can create 2 faces.

-Leg problems time to time

Discord server feel free to drop and say hi ^^
